{"tid":186394,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE GEOG 5* = 健心 + 掙扎！","createTime":"2017-04-04T07:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T10:01:10.000Z","uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52dbc49177af3936ba9a0d2666d15161af398451","tid":186394,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"GEOG 5*  120分鐘全方位掌握<br />\n<br />\n你只要高速GEOG技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要一堂，，足夠令你進入5*狀態！<br />\n<br />\nGEOG咁多課題，要全部背誦係無可能，而且無效率。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地著重的係點樣準備考試、點樣拆解唔同類型的問題、點樣調整心態面對考試的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n只要你有心，我就幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫你建立信心，培養5*的氣量！無論遇見咩題型，你都可以對答自如。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">地理地理，健心做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\ntelegram <br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/Scottish_Salmon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FScottish_Salmon&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pccn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6ec1f35c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/Scottish_Salmon</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>( 利申： AL + CE GEOG 皆A，熱衷地理教學&amp;分享心得，希望與有心有目標的學生攜手升靚U <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) </strong><br />\n====================<br />\n被問我答<br />\n<br />\n問：收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答：正正係要收<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">考評局</span>皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks 巴打<br />\n<br />\n問：點解係5*而唔係5**心態？<br />\n答：每個人都想富有。<br />\n<br />\n目標做百萬富翁，貼近現實；要每個人都目標做Bill Gates， 恐怕仲難過要胡師傅教踩單車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n====================<br />\n心態決定境界，2個鐘入面，你會學到你未接觸過的GEOG技巧、知識。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>5星，讓我們一起摘取！</strong>"},{"pid":"6915d882bb27fc22720d76a114a4fe453c08b8de","tid":186394,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,